To compile:
g++  -D_LARGEFILE64_SOURCE -fPIC -Wall -Werror -Wextra -Wno-unused-parameter -pthread -Wnon-virtual-dtor -g -fPIC -I/usr/local/src/build -I/usr/local/src/build/h -I/usr/local/src/CASTOR2 -I/usr/local/src/CASTOR2/h -I/usr/include/xrootd   -o c2stress /usr/local/src/CASTOR2/test/stressTest/c2stress.cpp -L /usr/lib64 -lcastorcommon -lcastorrfio -lcastorns -lcastorsecurity -lXrdCl

Example:
  STAGER_TRACE=0 c2stress --basedir /castor/cern.ch/user/s/sponcec3/tape/stress2114 --stager lxc2cert5 --svcclass default --nbthreads 20 --nbreads 1 --delay 0 --nbiterations 0 

Clients:
  castor/c2cert/c2cert5/diskserver/client
